# E-Kalolsavam Frontend Environment Configuration

# API Backend URL
# Default: http://localhost:8000
# Production: Update to your production backend URL
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

# Google OAuth 2.0 Client ID
# Required for Google Sign-In button to appear
# Get this from: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# IMPORTANT: This MUST match SOCIAL_AUTH_GOOGLE_OAUTH2_KEY in backend/.env
# Format: xxxxx-xxxxx.apps.googleusercontent.com
REACT_APP_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=

# ============================================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# ============================================================================
# 
# 1. Copy this file and rename to .env (remove .example)
#    Example: cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Get your Google OAuth Client ID:
#    - Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
#    - Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (or use existing one)
#    - Copy the Client ID
#
# 3. Paste your Client ID after REACT_APP_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
#    Example: REACT_APP_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=123456-abc.apps.googleusercontent.com
#
# 4. Verify it matches backend/.env:
#    - Open backend/.env
#    - Check SOCIAL_AUTH_GOOGLE_OAUTH2_KEY has the SAME value
#
# 5. Restart the frontend server:
#    npm start
#
# 6. Verify Google button appears:
#    - Navigate to http://localhost:3000/login
#    - You should see the Google Sign In button
#
# ============================================================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING:
# ============================================================================
#
# - Button not appearing?
#   → Make sure REACT_APP_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID has a value
#   → Restart frontend server (npm start)
#   → Clear browser cache
#
# - "Invalid token" error?
#   → Verify Client ID matches between frontend and backend .env
#   → Check for extra spaces or quotes
#
# - "Email not authorized"?
#   → Add email to allowed list in Admin Panel
#
# See RESTORE_GOOGLE_LOGIN.md for complete documentation
# ============================================================================
